--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-11-26)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (nginx_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.2.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-04-30)
E: Improve indentation of log_formats

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-04-30)
F: Add option to define log_format main (nginx_log_format_main)
F: Add option to define log_format main_ssl (nginx_log_format_main_ssl)

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-04-18)
E: Enable TLS version 1.3 by default

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-03-17)
F: Initial release
